 />\n<br />\n中途上機係唔得, 因為以前就係太多人好似你咁諗<br />\n而家個玩法轉咗做買多程短途(e.g. 台灣/廣州)再飛英國咁就會平<br />\n<br />\ne.g. 廣州&gt;香港&gt;倫敦"},{"pid":"f3b183ff9380b1e832a21f8def0facfa0abfb038","tid":958000,"uid":39838,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"da61eb48d74d757fe7660bb68c006646620764d4","tid":958000,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T13:04:31.000Z","msg":"巴里島飛香港程機如果坐唔滿 航空公司要罰錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T13:09:45.000Z","msg":"坐唔滿頂多蝕錢啫<br />\n佢地鐘意運空氣嘅邊個罰佢錢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dab5b24d8b8690c0008faff5aaa35c529c71585f","tid":958000,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T13:29:44.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"e7aa2b2668826dbbee20893307a98de9c7403661","tid":958000,"uid":226713,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a8133db391409e7407e057d5c9f0b5e4dd995a5f","tid":958000,"uid":11526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"90def71c648f33c2d5c0fc25bec69585172dc9dd","tid":958000,"uid":39838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"903e7e476175d77927580c61552335974374549b","tid":958000,"uid":11526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T12:38:36.000Z","msg":"係香港直飛倫敦要$6879<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OCthVkh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOCthVkh.png&h=9b209d2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.trip.com/flights/Booking/729359a3548c2eb2b7267f1a1c4f6650?flighttype=OW&amp;DCity=HKG&amp;ACity=LON&amp;DDate=2019-06-04&amp;Quantity=1&amp;ChildQty=0&amp;BabyQty=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.trip.com%2Fflights%2FBooking%2F729359a3548c2eb2b7267f1a1c4f6650%3Fflighttype%3DOW%26DCity%3DHKG%26ACity%3DLON%26DDate%3D2019-06-04%26Quantity%3D1%26ChildQty%3D0%26BabyQty%3D0&d=wP1V4d3dEokp1rN2RNzFf0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=0ed033f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.trip.com/flights/Booking/729359a3548c2eb2b7267f1a1c4f66